{ By Susan Gray For Weekend Magazine   Published:  22:30, 21 February 2020   https://www.dailymail.co.uk//femail/article-8017445/My-life-lens-Clive-Anderson-67-shares-stories-favourite-snaps.html }
Celebrities share the stories behind their favourite photographs. This week it’s TV and radio host Clive Anderson, 67. As told to Susan Gray. Clive’s show Me, Macbeth & I is on tour from 13 March to 24 May. He’ll present series two of Mystic Britain on the Smithsonian Channel later this year.  
